	   <tr><td colspan=2>The effects of many songs continue for a few seconds after you have stoped singing / playing them.&nbsp;&nbsp;Twisting is when you can time the start of your songs to allow the effects of them all to act at the same time, and restart each song before the effects wear off.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
